Package: loadtestframework
Version: 1.0.0
Section: testing
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-venv, python3-pip, ca-certificates, curl, build-essential, cmake, git, libncurses5-dev, libssl-dev, libpcap-dev, libnet1-dev, libsctp-dev, lksctp-tools, libgsl-dev, pkg-config, libpq-dev, python3-pyqt5
Maintainer: Shikhar <shikhar.gangwar@honeywell.com>
Description: Load Test Framework
 A comprehensive load testing framework supporting speed tests,
 web browsing, video streaming, and VoIP (SIPp) protocols.
 Includes a PyQt5 GUI and CLI mode with Docker-based test orchestration.
